olor:#000000;font-size:40px;font-style:normal;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:1px\">From Passion to Performance!</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#000000\"},\"elements\":{\"link\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#000000\"}}},\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"18px\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-text-color has-link-color\" style=\"color:#000000;font-size:18px\">Mojoju started with a simple love for music and a dream to share that passion with the world. Our journey began in local clubs, where the infectious beats of house, afro house, and Latin house ignited a fire within us. Each set was not just a performance but a celebration of life and energy. As we played for friends and strangers alike, we discovered the magic of connecting through rhythm. This inspired us to take our sound to festivals, where the vibe is electric and the crowd is ready to dance. Today, we’re not just DJs; we’re storytellers through sound, helping others find their own groove along the way.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:buttons {\"style\":{\"layout\":{\"selfStretch\":\"fit\",\"flexSize\":null},\"spacing\":{\"margin\":{\"top\":\"30px\"}}},\"layout\":{\"type\":\"flex\",\"justifyContent\":\"center\",\"flexWrap\":\"wrap\",\"orientation\":\"horizontal\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons\" style=\"margin-top:30px\"><!-- wp:button {\"width\":25,\"className\":\"is-style-fill\",\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"textTransform\":\"uppercase\",\"fontSize\":\"1.01rem\",\"lineHeight\":\"1.5\",\"fontStyle\":\"normal\",\"fontWeight\":\"600\",\"letterSpacing\":\"1px\"},\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"left\":\"0.31rem\",\"right\":\"0.31rem\",\"top\":\"0.71rem\",\"bottom\":\"0.71rem\"}},\"color\":{\"text\":\"#fffffd\",\"background\":\"#e27013\"},\"border\":{\"width\":\"0px\",\"style\":\"none\",\"radius\":\"0rem\"}},\"fontFamily\":\"pontano-sans\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-button has-custom-width wp-block-button__width-25 is-style-fill\"